Actions.Text: REPORTED REFERRED TO WAYS AND MEANS

Votes.VoteType: Favorable refer to committee Ways and Means

Title: Authorizes Greene county to enter into an agreement with a contiguous county to share the construction, financing, improvement, maintenance and/or housing of certain persons of a county jail
Summary: Authorizes Greene county to enter into an agreement with a contiguous county to share the construction, financing, improvement, maintenance and/or housing of persons in the custody of the sheriff of a county jail.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to authorizing Greene county to enter into an agreement with a contiguous county to share the construction, financing, improvement, maintenance and/or housing of persons in the custody of the sheriff of a county jail
